<h2 id="section-top">What we offer</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel three-sm">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn2">
</div>
<div class="col tertiary-content">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-11">General</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="not-answered">Accepting new clients <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Accepting referrals from Local Authority(s)<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">Accepting self-funded clients <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Day care<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">Emergency care <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Respite care<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContentf4b146c5acac49239e6f06b9aed09d26">
</div>
<p>Agincare’s excellent reputation for providing high quality and person centred services is achieved through not having a ‘one size fits all’ approach to our service provision. Our ethos is to provide a holistic service, which enables you to maintain full control and choice with your care so it fits around your chosen lifestyle and preferences. As such Agincare offers the following types of care provision</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.agincare.com/" target="_blank" title="Agincare Domiciliary Care">Domiciliary Care</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.liveincare.info/" target="_blank" title="Agincare Live-in Care ">Live-in Care</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.agincare-homes.co.uk/chalgrove-care-nursing-home-poole-dorset" target="_blank" title="Chalgrove Care and Nursing Home in Poole Dorset">Care Homes</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.agincare.com/" target="_self" title="Agincare Home Cuisine">Home Cuisine</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.liveincare.info/young-people/personal-assistants" target="_blank" title="Agincare Live-in Care Young adult care">Young Adult      Care </a></li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
