<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-15">Care at home - Personal</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Companionship<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Hourly visiting care<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Live in care workers<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Mobility support at home<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">Mobility support outside the home <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Personal and intimate care<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContentcb11781911dc45769e72ae560f8647f2">
</div>
<p><a href="http://www.agincare.com/domiciliary-home-care-living-independently/"><strong>DOMICILIARY CARE</strong></a><strong><br/> </strong>Maintain independence with as much or as little home care support on a daily basis.<br/> <a href="http://www.agincare.com/domiciliary-home-care-living-independently" target="_self" title="Domiciliary Care from Agincare">&gt;&gt;Agincare UK website</a><strong></strong></p>
<p><a href="http://www.liveincare.info/"><strong>LIVE-IN CARE</strong></a><strong><br/> </strong>Enables low to high dependency care clients to continue living in their own home.<br/> <a href="http://www.liveincare.info/">&gt;&gt;Live-in Care website</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.agincare.com/home-cuisine-care-meal-delivery"><strong>HOME CUISINE</strong></a><strong><br/> </strong>Delivery of hot, nutritious meals to clients in their own homes with a daily care check.<br/> <a href="http://www.agincare.com/home-cuisine-care-meal-delivery" title="Agincare Home Cuisine">&gt;&gt;Home Cusine info</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.agincare-homes.com/"><strong>CARE HOMES</strong></a><strong><br/> </strong>Provideing the best possible care for people with dementia or mental health conditions.<br/> <a href="http://www.agincare-homes.com/">&gt;&gt;Care Homes website</a></p>
